          JSON DataFilter This DataFilter walks an Object as if it was a call to JSON.toString(Object) and calls the protected methods JSONDataFilter.filterString(String), JSONDataFilter.filterNumber(Number), JSONDataFilter.filterBoolean(Boolean), JSONDataFilter.filterArray(Object, Client) or JSONDataFilter.filterMap(Map, Client) appropriate.
